<title>Full Text</title>
<para id="fs-idm406104944">July 10, 1832: Bank Veto (transcript) <link url="http://teachingamericanhistory.org/library/document/veto-of-the-civil-rights-bill/">http://teachingamericanhistory.org/library/document/veto-of-the-civil-rights-bill/</link></para>
