<problem id="fs-idm411512256">
<para id="fs-idm394380592">According to Johnson, why might four million newly freed people not deserve the “privileges and immunities of citizenship?”</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm392523904">
<problem id="fs-idm358438976">
<para id="fs-idm407407072">According to Johnson, how does this act change the previous process of gaining citizenship?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm392472880">
<problem id="fs-idm405740096">
<para id="fs-idm400845328">Why does Johnson despise the part of the Civil Rights Act that guarantees protection for the freedmen?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
